%% ===== 历史折叠展开时序图（R3，核心链路）=====
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 用户
    participant HF as HistoryFragment
    participant HA as HistoryAdapter
    participant VH as ViewHolder(binding)
    participant RF as ResultFormatter

    Note over HF,HA: onResume → load() → new HistoryAdapter(list)
    HF->>HA: 构造(list)  // 无 onClick 参数（showDetail 已移除）
    HA->>HA: expanded = MutableList(size){false}

    Note over HA,VH: onBindViewHolder(position)
    HA->>VH: tvSummary.text = item.summary  // one-liner，折叠/展开均显示
    HA->>RF: displayTextFor(item)
    RF-->>VH: 完整可读中文（displayText 或回退 detailJson）
    HA->>VH: tvDetail.text = 完整文本
    HA->>VH: tvDetail.visibility = expanded[position] ? VISIBLE : GONE
    HA->>VH: ivArrow.rotation = expanded[position] ? 180f : 0f

    U->>VH: 点击 itemView(position)
    VH->>HA: itemView 点击监听触发
    HA->>HA: expanded[position] = !expanded[position]
    HA->>HA: notifyItemChanged(position)  // 局部刷新
    HA->>VH: 重新 onBindViewHolder → 切换 tvDetail 显隐 + 箭头旋转

%% ===== R2 下拉（已存在，本次仅回归验收，非开发时序）=====
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as 用户
    participant F as Body/FoodAnalysisFragment
    participant PD as UserProfileDao
    participant AP as AppPreferences
    participant ACT as MaterialAutoCompleteTextView(autoProfile)

    Note over F: onViewCreated → loadProfilesAndSetupDropdown()
    F->>PD: getAll()
    PD-->>F: List<UserProfile>
    F->>AP: getActiveProfileId()
    AP-->>F: activeId
    alt activeId 存在且档案在列
        F->>F: effectiveId = activeId
    else 无 active 但有人建档
        F->>AP: setActiveProfileId(firstId)
        F->>F: effectiveId = firstId
    else 无人建档
        F->>F: effectiveId = 0L（通用建议）
    end
    F->>ACT: setAdapter(通用建议 + 全档案)
    F->>ACT: setText(selectedName, false)
    U->>ACT: 展开下拉
    ACT-->>U: 列出「通用建议」+ 全档案
    U->>ACT: 选择某项
    ACT->>F: setOnItemClickListener → selectedProfileId = 选项.id
    Note right of F: selectedProfileId 仅本次分析生效，\n不写回 activeProfileId
